snippet.title: Kill It With Fire - Release Date Trailer [August 13]
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1179210/Kill_It_With_Fire/ - Pre-Order / Wishlist Now! August 13 will be a terrible day for spiders worldwide. 

Kill It With Fire is a first-person action game about hunting spiders and causing collateral damage.

Free demo available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1291500/Kill_It_With_Fire_Ignition/

Extended gameplay: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BFTIuzp-5zw&feature=youtu.be

#KILLITWITHFIRE #Spiders #Arachnophobia
